docApp.directive('docRelatedApplicationDtv', ['$timeout','$http','$compile','docCmmUtilFct', 'docCmmFct', 'docCmmLinkFct', function($timeout, $http, $compile, docCmmUtilFct, docCmmFct, docCmmLinkFct){
	return {
		restrict: 'A',
		link : 	postLink  //compile 이 등록되어 있으면 link 는 수행하지 않는다.
	};
	
	function preCompile(scope, elm, attrs, ctrl){
		/**
		 * 변수 초기화
		 */
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.skey = scope.docVar.screenVO.skey;
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.sortType = "DESC";
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum = 1;
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageRow = scope.docConst.REL_APPL_PAGE_ROW;
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList = [
			                       		       {id:'chk', fieldNm:'', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //check
			                       		     , {id:'ORG', fieldNm:'원문', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //원문
			                       		     , {id:'STATUS', fieldNm:'유형', sortField:'ctry', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //국가
			                       		     , {id:'AN', fieldNm:'출원번호', sortField:'appl_num', sortType:'ASC', arrClass:'ico_arralign ico_default', thClass:'tb_head_backcolor'}   //문서번호
			                       		     , {id:'AD', fieldNm:'출원일자', sortField:'appl_dt', sortType:'DESC', arrClass:'ico_arralign ico_default', thClass:'tb_head_backcolor'}   //일자
			                       		     , {id:'TI', fieldNm:'발명의 명칭', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //발명의 명칭
			                       		];
		
		// 전체 카운트
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt = 0;
		// 전체 페이지수 
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt = 1;
		// 보유 건수
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt = 0;
		// 미보유 건수 
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount = 0;
		// all skey list
		scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.allSkeys = "";
		
		scope.findRelApplList = function() {
			var url = "";
			
			if(scope.docVar.screenVO.ctry == 'KR') {
				url = "../dkr/findRelatedApplication.wips";
			} else if(scope.docVar.screenVO.ctry == 'EP') {
				url = "../dep/findRelatedApplication.wips";
			} else if(scope.docVar.screenVO.ctry == 'WO') {
				url = "../dwo/findRelatedApplication.wips";
			} else if(scope.docVar.screenVO.ctry == 'JP') {
				url = "../djp/findRelatedApplication.wips";
			}
			
			var obj = { skey : scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.skey
						, sortType : scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.sortType
						, pageNum:scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum
						, pageRow:scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageRow
					  };

			$http.post(url, $.param(obj),{
				headers: {'Content-Type': scope.docConst.JSON_CONT_TYPE}
			}).success(function(data){
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.allChk = false;
				// 보유목록
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList = data.relApplTextList;
				
				//checkbox 초기화
				for(var i=0; i < scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList.length; i++){
					scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList[i].chk = false;
				}
				
				// Provisional of 목록
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.provisionalList = data.provisionalList;
				// 미보유 목록
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.missingList = data.missingList;
				// 전체 건수 = 보유 건수 + 미보유 건수 + provisional 건수
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt = data.relApplTextList.length + data.provisionalList.length + data.missingCnt.missingDocCount;
				
				// 전체 페이지
				if(data.relApplCnt.totalPage != 0) {
					scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt = data.relApplCnt.totalPage;
				}
				// 미보유 건수
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount = data.missingCnt.missingDocCount;
				
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum;
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageRow = scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageRow;
				
				// 전체 skeys
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.maxSkeys = data.skeys;
				
				scope.clickDevBtnMarker();
				scope.docQueryHighLighter($("form#paramForm :input[name=hl]").val());
				
				// 상세보기 오른쪽 메뉴 레이어 메뉴 수정
				if(scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt > 0){
					scrollRightSet("devRA", "Related Appl.");
				}
			}).error(function(data, status){
				/*if (/EgovBizException/.test(data.responseText)) {
		            alert(data.responseText.match(/EgovBizException: &quot;(.*?)&quot;/)[1]);
		            // error 처리
		        }
		        else {
		            alert("에러가 발생하였습니다. " + status + "\nError: " + data.responseText);
		        }*/
			});
			
		};
		
		
		/**
		 * 헤더에서 소트키 클릭시
		 */
		scope.relApplListSort = function(headerIndex){
			if(scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.sortType === "DESC") {
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.sortType = "ASC";
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].arrClass = "ico_arralign ico_arrup";
				//scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].thClass = "tb_head_backcolor font_color_orange";
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].fontClass = "font_color_orange";
			} else {
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.sortType = "DESC";
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].arrClass = "ico_arralign ico_arrdown";
//				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].thClass = "tb_head_backcolor font_color_orange";
				scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].fontClass = "font_color_orange";
			}
			
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};
		
		/**
		 * 이전페이지 클릭시
		 */
		scope.prevPageRelAppl = function(){
			if(scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum == 1){
				return;
			}
			
			scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum - 1;
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};
		
		/**
		 * 다음페이지 클릭시
		 */
		scope.nextPageRelAppl = function(){
			if(scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum == scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt){
				return;
			}
			
			scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.docRelApplVO.docRelApplParamVO.pageNum + 1;
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};
		
		//원문 아이콘 class
		scope.pdfIconClass = function(pdfGb, ctry) {
			if(ctry == "CA"){
				pdfGb = 0;
			}
			
			if(pdfGb == 1 || pdfGb == 2) {
				return 'btn_openpdf';
			}
			else { // null
				return "btn_dispdf";
			}
		};

	};
	
	function postLink(scope, elm, attrs, ctrl){
		preCompile(scope, elm, attrs, ctrl);
		elm.empty();
		var innerHtml = docCmmUtilFct.hereDoc(function() {/*!
					<div class="devHighlightNg" ng-if="docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList.length > 0 || docVar.docRelApplVO.provisionalList.length > 0 || docVar.docRelApplVO.missingList.length > 0">
                        
                        <div class="dc_leftblock">
                            <span class="first_line">Related Application</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="dc_context_block">
                        	<div class="float_l">
                                <span class="float_l marg_right_20">전체 <span class="font_type_bold page_backcolor_step1_text font_valign_00" ng-bind="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt"></span> 건</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="float_r">
                               <div class="paginate_type3 pagenate_align">
                                	<span class="pagenum"><span ng-bind="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageNum"></span>/<span ng-bind="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt"></span></span>
                                    <a ng-if="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt > 1" href="javascript:void(0);" ng-click="prevPageRelAppl();">
                                    	<span class="direction"><span class="prev"><!-- --></span><span class="ir_pm">이전</span></span>
                                    </a>
                                    <span ng-if="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt <= 1"> 
                                    	<span class="direction btn_dis_type"><span class="prev"><!-- --></span><span class="ir_pm">이전</span></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <a ng-if="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt > 1" href="javascript:void(0);" ng-click="nextPageRelAppl();">
                                    	<span class="direction"><span class="next"><!-- --></span><span class="ir_pm">다음</span></span>
                                    </a>
                                    <span ng-if="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt <= 1"> 
                                    	<span class="direction btn_dis_type"><span class="next"><!-- --></span><span class="ir_pm">다음</span></span>
                                    </span> 
                                </div>
                           </div>
                           <div class="clear"><!-- --></div>
                            <table class="marg_top_05 table_type2 oneline_width devDocViewOption">
                                <colgroup>
                                    <col width="30">
                                    <col width="50">
                                    <col width="130">
                                    <col width="130">
                                    <col width="110">
                                    <col width="*">
                                </colgroup>
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor">No</th>
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor">원문</th>
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor">유형</th>
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor">출원번호</th> 
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor"><a href="javascript:void(0);" ng-click="relApplListSort(4)" ng-class="docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[4].fontClass"><span ng-bind-html="docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[4].fieldNm"></span><span ng-class="docVar.docRelApplVO.headerList[4].arrClass"><!-- --></span></a></th>
	                                    <th class="tb_head_backcolor font_align_left">발명의 명칭</th>
                                	</tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr ng-show="docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList.length == 0">
                                		<td colspan="6" class="font_align_center">
                                			<p>해당 정보가 없습니다.</p>
                                		</td>
                                	</tr>
                                   	<tr ng-show="docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList.length > 0" ng-repeat="relAppl in docVar.docRelApplVO.rsltList">
                                        <td class="font_align_center" ng-bind="((docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageNum - 1) * docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageRow) + $index+1"></td>
                                        <td class="font_align_center">
                                        	<a ng-hide="relAppl.pdfGb == '0'" doc-pdf-rel-appl-dtv ng-model="docVar.screenVO.ctry" pdf-skey="{{relAppl.skey}}" ng-class="pdfIconClass(relAppl.pdfGb, relAppl.ctry) + ' marg_auto marg_top_05'"><span class="screen_hide">PDF</span></a>
                                        	<span ng-show="relAppl.pdfGb == '0'" ng-class="pdfIconClass(relAppl.pdfGb, relAppl.ctry) + ' marg_auto marg_top_05'"><span class="screen_hide">PDF</span></span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="font_align_center" ng-bind-html="relAppl.desc"></td>
                                        
                                        <td class="font_align_center">
                                        	<a ng-hide="relAppl.skey == null || relAppl.skey == ''" doc-link-dtv ng-model="relAppl"><span ng-bind-html="relAppl.applNum"></span></a>
                                        	<span ng-show="relAppl.skey == null || relAppl.skey == ''" ng-bind-html="relAppl.applNum"></span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="font_align_center"><span ng-bind-html="relAppl.applDt"></span></td>
                                        <td>
                                        	<a ng-hide="relAppl.skey == null || relAppl.skey == ''" doc-link-dtv ng-model="relAppl"><span ng-bind-html="relAppl.invTi"></span></a>
                                        	<span ng-show="relAppl.skey == null || relAppl.skey == ''" ng-bind-html="relAppl.invTi"></span>
                                        </td>
                                   </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                            <div class="remark_footblock">
                              <p ng-hide="docVar.docRelApplVO.provisionalList.length <= 0">
                              	<span class="title_text">* Provisional</span>
                              	<span ng-repeat="provision in docVar.docRelApplVO.provisionalList"> 
                                 <span ng-class="{'font_color_888': true, 'text_divbar': !$last, 'float_l': $last}" ng-bind-html="provision.ctry + ' ' + provision.applNum + ' ' + provision.applDt"></span>
                                </span>
                              </p> 
                              <p ng-hide="docVar.docRelApplVO.missingList.length <= 0">
                              	<span class="title_text2">* 미포함 문헌 : <span ng-bind="docVar.docRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount" ></span>건 (절차상 미공개 문헌, 과거분 문헌, WIPS 보유 데이터 범위에 포함되지 않는 문헌)</span>
                                <span ng-repeat="missing in docVar.docRelApplVO.missingList"> 
                                 <span ng-class="{'font_color_888': true, 'text_divbar': !$last, 'float_l': $last}" ng-bind-html="missing.ctry + ' ' + missing.applNum + ' ' + missing.applDt"></span>
                                 </span>
                              </p> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="list_space"><!-- --></div>
                        
                        </div>
					</div> 
                */
		});
		
		elm.html($compile(innerHtml)(scope));
		scope.findRelApplList();
	};
	
	
}]);